Its about time we had some festive gift wrap! Mister McGinnis returns with his avante-garde-kitsch holiday gift wrap. 

This set contains four fresh designs to bring out the jolly in your holiday season.
Each sheet is 24" x 36"

1. Chests, Nuts, & Fire offers your friends and family just that, and with plenty of fire.

2. A Very Hairy Christmas - What better way to warm up than with the gift of a furry, bearded man.

3. He Watches you - This reminds you of the grim reality that an old man is watching you at the office party this Christmas.

4. Donner on Blitzen - Theyâ€™re some frisky little fellas..

name: A is for Atomic
description:
Remember those alphabet cards we played with as kids? Well Mister McGinnis has hand screen printed the entire alphabet. All colors are custom mixed and each letter has a little twist. There's a letter for everyone. Well... almost everyone.

Atomic is printed with 4 colors. The print is 14" x 20" and silk screened on French Smart White cover. Each print is signed and numbered. 
When Mister McGinnis prints a new edition, he will change colors and/or update the image to ensure each edition is limited and unique for each buyer. He usually prints in editions of 60 or less.

If purchasing a framed print, the frame is made of white ash and its outside dimensions are 17" x 23".

name: Master Debaters Set 2
description:
These cards speak volumes. A collection of American and other cultural symbols, characters and topics relentlessly pursued by the media. Why read the newspaper when you can create your very own biased conversations by placing one next to the other.

Printed on heavy uncoated recycled card stock, perforated on the folds so you can tear them apart into different configurations. Comes with three envelopes in a plastic box.
